attr.title: TS Underswap
attr.desc:
TS!Underswap is an unofficial fan-made reimagining of Toby Fox's UNDERTALE, made by Team Switched (TS).

The official DEMO features the first two areas, Ruined Home and Starlight Isles!
attr.inst: Download the Windows version from https://gamejolt.com/games/tsunderswap/160094 and unzip to `ports/tsunderswap/gamedata`
